Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:47.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空  赤く染める  黒檀の闇　呑み込まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:59.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星屑たち　儚く 降り積もる　灰の雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:10.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見つめた　嘆きの窓　I never dreamed　凍りつく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}there… I come for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:18.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想いは　寂寞の夜空に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:23.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}舞い上がり　砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:30.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界が 形を変えるたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:39.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}守りたいものを壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}しまっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:47.72,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空 染血紅 黑檀之暗 吞噬殆盡無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:59.22,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星塵 如幻夢 紛揚而下 堆積灰雪叢叢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:10.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}久久凝視  歎息的窗口 I never dreamed 徹骨霜凍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.69,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}there… I come for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:18.47,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰的思念 在寂寞的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:23.52,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}起舞而上 破碎凋零隨風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:30.69,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這個世界 每次變換身形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:39.56,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}都把守護之物 片片擊碎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.92,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再也無法觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:25.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:33.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う景色を　受け入れられずに　もがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:41.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:46.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:48.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:58.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:07.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:12.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:18.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:23.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:31.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:25.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經久不變的笑顏　是這樣的我們　在年輪中週而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:33.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而過的風景　卻無法剪下收藏　唯心房中絲縷焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:41.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將無謂的自尊遠遠拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:46.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用溫柔將這個世界抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:48.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告訴我你的勇氣　即使逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:58.31,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一個人便無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:07.78,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於我心深處　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:12.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:18.48,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為不能忘記 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:23.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:31.03,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這片無垠大地和同伴們的故事


Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙向通信系統 預定地點全部設置完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EURO 2來電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始散佈浮游型雙向通信系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接入UNION 3的網絡通信狀況良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.35,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}人革聯 塔克拉瑪干沙漠駐屯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模擬計劃 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加演習的所有部隊 通信網的連接確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有MS的通信情況 良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到啊 會有一天和UNION與AEU聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 機體的防塵情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切順利 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看好吧 我這架機體鐵定把Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白日做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.48,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UNION軍 沖繩近海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags部隊 在命令下達前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部隊總數52支 參加MS 832架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便罵我是卑鄙小人 也請允許我遵從軍隊的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 你那個樣子要到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽回去了 人家沒心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請鼓勵我下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來哦 露易…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質上的鼓勵 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買不起啊 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的名牌首飾 怎麼買得起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了我 買嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買啊買啊 買給我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呀 那兩個孩子 {\a6}買給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無憂無慮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明現在有近千架MS在進行大規模演習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是異常情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大規模演習 也在你的計劃之內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.58,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}人革聯 國家主席官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次說的事情怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從情報部發來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告稱 三架MS以及三輛人員運輸車 正在前往濃縮鈾的埋藏地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是等他們自投羅網…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習地域裡配置的雙向通信系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現障礙反映
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把作戰的變更傳達給司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是飽受輿論的非難 提供了演習的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差也得弄到兩架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 維持速度和高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搖晃機體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要強人所難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測班 Gundam在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信屏蔽點的線路上 沒有駐屯部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.29,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AEU 塔克拉瑪干沙漠前線基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 Gundam正在前往濃縮鈾的埋藏地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 恐怖分子正在向設施移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 司令部發來俘獲Gundam的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切是精心策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說為誘騙Gundam 政府掌握著恐怖分子的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意放他們進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 目標瞄準開火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部命中 全部命中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要脫離了 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.77,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我全力炮擊 把Gundam釘死在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過第一階段的預計結束時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能安全撤離的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪的預測是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕事態在向B2計劃發展中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Exia與Virtur投入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION 3 初期進攻成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 2機 位於JF4122
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續遠距離炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 遠距離炮擊 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HUMAN 1傳來可視暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求向TF2123派送增援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然瞄準了兵力少的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓第二十三MS部隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三MS部隊 立即出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三MS部隊 立即出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 為什麼不向我下達出擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在待機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你成為男子漢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務計劃進入B2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 外裝甲迷彩膜解凍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現Gundam 2機 快向總部聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtur 確保撤退路線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN火炮 暴風模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子壓縮率 97%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入B2計劃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 開始裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這數量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始至今已經2小時了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按B2計劃 Dynames與Kyrios應該快到會合地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果至少GN兵裝能使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從時間看 B2計劃正向E5過渡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的話 那架機體會來 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公告裡提到的人革專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.81,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你們得逞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離裝填完畢還有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有170秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次 這一次 一定要完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵一號 索瑪 皮瑞斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做索瑪·皮瑞斯阿 真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有殺掉的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給你了 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥開始後已經過了五個小時了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聽聽其他觀察者們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作可能也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人真讓人討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7MS小隊達到活動時間的界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由第16MS小隊接替
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上場的機會就要來了 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的攻擊還要持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總得給點吃飯的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會把Gundam交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OverFlag隊 任務時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 古拉哈姆·艾卡 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達各機 我們的目標是那個大傢伙Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊停止的同時 我們開始俘獲作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被敵人的光束擊中阿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 戰鬥開始後已經15個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 你的動作很遲鈍 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹的好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了本大爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 已虜獲帶翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還會像以前那樣突然動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官 目標已視線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E陣形開始任務!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 約修亞他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約修亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要破壞陣形!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副隊長的臭架子!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中變形?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想要自己獨吞嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊…什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約修亞他!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變更為陣形C!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指尖的感覺已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入我的懷抱吧 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我的睡美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師們的聯絡怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在逝去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam機師們的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的 機師們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點鐘方向出現敵影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mobile Armor…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Enact是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次欠的讓我好好地來償還一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊?Gundam先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊 Agristor等離子場的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我留下機體消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯的小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是外交部傳來的非正式消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歐大陸上進行的聯合演習途中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織似乎出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像雙方已經進入交戰狀態了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 面對有近千架MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑四架Gundam就來挑戰什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這個世界如此扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的錯 還是人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個扭曲的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一事無成…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣不斷失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐朽風化掉麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…d…a…m…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…G…u…n…d…a…m…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Gun…dam…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Gun…dam…!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne 嶄新登場的Gundam三機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:37.39,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Throne：天使中排名上級第三位的座天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們放出的 閃耀著GN粒子光芒之物是?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:43.66,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,930)}Trinity
